Package org.cip4.elk.alces.preprocessor.jmf

Interface Summary
Preprocessor This class preprocesses JMF messages.
 

Class Summary
JMFPreprocessor Deprecated. This Preprocessor has ben split up into separate preprocessors for the different types of preprocessing.
MessageIDPreprocessor Preprocesses a JMF message by replacing message IDs (/JMF/Message/@ID) with unique IDs.
SenderIDPreprocessor Preprocesses a JMF message by replacing JMF/@SenderID.
TimeStampPreprocessor Preprocesses a JMF message by replacing JMF/@TimeStamp
URLPreprocessor A preprocessor that replaces the following attributes with URL values with a specified URL: //@ReturnJMF //@ReturnURL //@AcknowledgeURL //jdf:Subscription/@URL //jdf:StopPersChParams/@URL
XPathPreprocessor A preprocessor that sets a node selected by an XPaths to a new value.
